race.comment: ALAQEEQ (4) First start at the races 2yo by Good Magic for trainer Sami Alharabi. Jockey Ricardo Ferreira is highly regarded. Market as guide. THU ALWASHAH (18) 2yo debutant sired by Flame Away for Bader Rizaiq. Watch the betting. RA AEE ALAWALA (24) Competitive effort when 2nd last time at this venue. Looks promising in this race. AL NOMAS (3) Ran 2nd last run at the track and was a debutant last start. Going up in distance. Genuine winning chance.
